author: GameSpot
description:
PlayStation Portal owners can now stream their games from the cloud, Sony has announced. After rolling out a beta version last year, the updated version of Cloud Streaming will allow PS Plus Premium members to play a massively expanded selection of games on the device, and it won't require them to connect to a PS5 console through Remote Play.

#playstationportal #cloudstreaming #gamespot
title: PlayStation Portal Finally Gets Full Cloud Streaming

author: GameSpot
description: The Counter Strike skin market has crashed. But how do their current prices stack up against things like groceries for a year? Or how about a 2016 Honda Civic? Kurt and Lucy try to guess.
title: What's More Expensive That Counter Strike Skins?
